      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat</p><p>Drain your <strong>sweetcorn</strong></p><p>Once the pan is hot, add the <strong>drained sweetcorn</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until starting to char</p><p>Tip: Keep an eye on the pan to make sure you don't burn the corn!</p>",
