    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pan is hot, add the <strong>spice-coated salmon fillets</strong>, skin-side down</p><p>Cook for 9-10 min, turning once halfway, or until cooked through – this is your<strong> blackened salmon</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1724396860497-x200.jpg",
