      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>mayo</strong> with the juice<strong> </strong>of <strong>half</strong> your<strong> lime[s]</strong> and 2 tsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tsp]</span> [4 tsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> in a small bowl – this is your <strong>lime dressing</strong></p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Remove the base of your<strong> lettuce </strong>then wash under <strong>cold running water</strong> and cut away the core, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Tear the <strong>lettuce leaves</strong> from the stem until you are left with a pile of leaves</p>",
      "order": 6,
