      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sweetcorn has charred, add the<strong> remaining lime juice</strong> to the pan with your <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and a pinch of <strong>black pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>charred chilli corn</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
